"/></g></g><g data-cell-id="1O9ielblsHRyez44P_6X-3"><g><rect x="40" y="28.5" width="410" height="180" fill="none" stroke="none" pointer-events="all"/></g><g><g><switch><foreignObject style="overflow: visible; text-align: left;" pointer-events="none" width="100%" height="100%" requiredFeatures="http://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/feature#Extensibility"><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="display: flex; align-items: unsafe center; justify-content: unsafe flex-start; width: 408px; height: 1px; padding-top: 119px; margin-left: 42px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 0; text-align: left; color: #000000; "><div style="display: inline-block; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;; color: #000000; line-height: 1.2; pointer-events: all; white-space: normal; word-wrap: normal; "><font style="font-size: 14px;" data-font-src="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Source+Sans+Pro">Hello Dave,</font><div><font style="font-size: 14px;" data-font-src="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Source+Sans+Pro"><br /></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14px;" data-font-src="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Source+Sans+Pro">I hope you had a great holiday and weekend.</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14px;" data-font-src="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Source+Sans+Pro"><br /></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14px;" data-font-src="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Source+Sans+Pro">When you get a chance, could you please send over the Q1 finance report?<br /><br />Thank you,</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14px;" data-font-src="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Source+Sans+Pro"><br /></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14px;" data-font-src="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Source+Sans+Pro">Steven - Accounting</font></div></div></div></div></foreignObject><image x="42" y="35.5" width="408" height="171" xlink:href="data:image/png;base64,"/></switch></g></g></g><g data-cell-id="1O9ie